Package: overlay
Title: Render and Overlay ggplot2 and gt objects or Code Snippets with Perspective and Transparency
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Luis D.", "Verde Arregoitia", email = "luis@liomys.mx", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9520-6543"))
Description: Renders ggplot2 plots, gt tables, and carbon.js code images as 
    magick objects, applies optional perspective warp distortions, and 
    composites them over background images with transparency.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
